    "sections": [
        {
            "navLabel": "The Loop",
            "title": "University City & The Loop",
            "text": [
                "Delmar Boulevard, the spine of University City, hosts The Loop — a stretch of independent restaurants, music venues, bookstores, and coffee shops that has been called one of the great American main streets.",
                "Blueprint Coffee and Star Clipper anchor the bookend of the strip, drawing a mix of Washington University students, long-time residents, and visitors from across the metro."
            ],
            "scene": {
