        {
            "navLabel": "Maplewood",
            "title": "Maplewood — The Manchester Strip",
            "text": [
                "Maplewood occupies just 1.4 square miles but has an outsized personality. Manchester Road is its main artery — a lively corridor of craft breweries, eclectic boutiques, and some of the county's best independent food and coffee.",
                "Coma Coffee Roasters exemplifies the neighborhood's ethos: serious craft with a relaxed, unpretentious attitude."
            ],
            "scene": {
                "center": [
                    -90.319,
                    38.617
