        {
            "navLabel": "East St. Louis County",
            "title": "East St. Louis County",
            "text": [
                "East St. Louis County is a patchwork of historic suburbs, distinct neighborhoods, and communities that grew up alongside the railroad and the Mississippi. Each municipality has its own character — from the government towers of Clayton to the Victorian porches of Webster Groves.",
                "This story explores the cities, neighborhoods, coffee shops, and bookstores that give the area its texture and identity. Scroll down to explore the geography."
            ],
